title: Millennium Season 2
description: Frank Black is a person with a strange gift (or curse): he can see across the eyes of an assassin. In such a circumstance he has integrated in the past, the Group Millennium, an ultrasecret department of the government to solve very difficult cases of serial assassins. Lance Henriksen personified Frank Black, the protagonist of this series of Chris Carter, the same creator of X-FILES . In spite of having very good histories and a general level similar to that of his series relates (even his plots were tending to be blacker), MILLENNIUM did not have the popularity that X-FILES and one stopped expressing(emitting) at the end of his third season, 67 episodes having been filmed.
